<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<main class="py-20 bg-[#FDFBF7] px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl text-[#2D1D30]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Rebirth of a Queen is committed to protecting your privacy in compliance with the <strong>Data Protection Act, 2019 (Laws of Kenya)</strong>. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard the personal data you provide.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">2. Data We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us, including:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Contact Details:</strong> Full name and email address when you sign up or contact us.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information automatically collected via third-party analytics tools regarding how you interact with our website.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">3. Use of Third-Party Analytics</h2>
            <p>We use third-party analytics services (such as Google Analytics) to understand website traffic and user behavior. These providers use cookies to collect anonymized data. This helps us improve our services. You may opt out of these cookies via your browser settings.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">4. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure your data is secure against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration, in line with Kenyan legal standards.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Under the Data Protection Act, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data where applicable.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">6. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at 
                <a href="mailto:legal@therebirthofaqueen.com" class="text-[#522D59] font-bold hover:underline">legal@therebirthofaqueen.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
